        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I run content marketing without a writer?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. theStacc handles writing as part of the pipeline — 30 articles a month plus GBP + social, all auto-published. You don't need to write or hire a writer. The output ships with optimization and schema already done." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What's the cheapest content marketing stack for a small business?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Free Canva + free Buffer + free Mailchimp + Ubersuggest ($29). Total: $29/month. The trade-off is your time — you do all the work. theStacc Bundle at $167/mo includes the work done for you." }},
